title: World Religions - From Ancient History to the Present.pdf
description:
World Religions: From Ancient History to the Present
Facts on File | 1983 | 0871961296 | English | 532 pages | PDF | 55.6 MB

Written by internationally renowned experts and lavishly illustrated with hundreds of images, this magnificent volume encompasses not just religion itself, but its entire context.Over twenty world faiths are examined here, from the eleven "living religions" to those of Mesopotamia, Egypt, Greece, and Rome, as well as traditional African, early Australasian, and Andean beliefs
